Australia has made a mistake that cannot be reversed and a chance at fixing the problem has been lost.
Aussies trust their 'officials' too much & continue to be overly compliant - even when illogical regulations are imposed on them. Half the world already knows that we are experiencing the biggest medical emergency in history in this 'program'.
As people slowly get informed and wake up, they will experience the usual Shock, Anger and Denial of the truth ( that there is evil behind this program ).
The final stage will be accept what actually happened - but it may be too late for many.
The 'official' narrative is already in tatters.

Prepare for tribunals everywhere . . . .

snippet.textDisplay: It is all rather sad but the Serbian Tennis Star has created the whole problem for himself, not to mention seriously inconveniencing many others in the last couple of weeks, by being an Anti-Vaxxer and therefore an anti-social. If his beliefs are that strong, then they should have outweighed the risk of trying to enter another country whose rules are very similar to most others and stayed home. Will he do it all again at Roland Garros?
